接口 Flushable

所有已知实现类：
AssetFileDescriptor.AutoCloseOutputStream, BufferedOutputStream, BufferedWriter, ByteArrayOutputStream, CharArrayWriter, CheckedOutputStream, ChunkedOutputStream, CipherOutputStream, ContentLengthOutputStream, DataOutputStream, DeflaterOutputStream, DigestOutputStream, FileOutputStream, FileWriter, FilterOutputStream, FilterWriter, Formatter, GZIPOutputStream, IdentityOutputStream, JarOutputStream, ObjectOutputStream, OutputStream, OutputStreamWriter, ParcelFileDescriptor.AutoCloseOutputStream, PipedOutputStream, PipedWriter, PrintStream, PrintWriter, StringWriter, Writer, ZipOutputStream
public interface Flushable

Defines an interface for classes that can (or need to) be flushed, typically before some output processing is considered to be finished and the object gets closed.

从以下版本开始：
Android 1.0

方法摘要
 void flush()
          Flushes the object by writing out any buffered data to the underlying output.
 

方法详细信息

flush

void flush()
           throws IOException
Flushes the object by writing out any buffered data to the underlying output.

抛出：
IOException - if there are any issues writing the data.
